# phase00_part4_.env.example
#
# This is a TEMPLATE — it is safe to share and commit to GitHub because it
# contains no real secrets, just the NAMES of the values needed.
#
# To use it: copy this file's contents into a new file named exactly ".env"
# (no other text in the name, just the dot and "env") in the same folder,
# and fill in real values there. The real ".env" file should NEVER be
# committed to GitHub — that's what .gitignore is for (see the guide,
# Section 6.5).

DEMO_API_TOKEN=my-test-token-123
